com.ephox.editlive.view

Interface ViewMouseListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener, MouseListener

    public interface ViewMouseListener
extends MouseListener
    An interface to indicate that mouse events should be passed through to the view instead of just to the JTextPane. Event coordinates are relative to the JTextPane.

    • Method Summary

      • Methods inherited from interface java.awt.event.MouseListener

        mouseClicked, mouseEntered, mouseExited, mousePressed, mouseReleased
